      <title>Altice France 高级债权人寻求为期 6 个月的合作协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/altice-france-senior-creditors-seek-6-month-cooperation-pact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Altice France 的高级债权人正在债务重组谈判之前通过一项异常长期的合作协议来调整其利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/altice-france-senior-creditors-seek-6-month-cooperation-pact</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:19:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
