    <item>
      <title>在经历了几个月来最糟糕的两天之后，避险需求提振了国债</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/treasuries-surge-as-middle-east-tension-stokes-demand-for-havens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期中东战争升级刺激了避险需求，美国国债周五大幅上涨，弥补了美国通胀数据造成的每周大幅跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/treasuries-surge-as-middle-east-tension-stokes-demand-for-havens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:58:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗布斯塔咖啡因短缺担忧而创新高；可可跳跃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/robusta-coffee-hits-fresh-record-high-as-shortage-fears-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心产量下降将加剧咖啡豆短缺，罗布斯塔咖啡在伦敦攀升至新高。阿拉比卡品种也因基金买盘强劲而上涨，而可可则飙升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/robusta-coffee-hits-fresh-record-high-as-shortage-fears-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>矿石短缺满足需求复苏，铜价持续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lme-copper-rises-to-highest-since-june-2022-as-outlook-brightens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价继续上涨，触及 2022 年 6 月以来的最高水平，因为投资者押注减少的矿石供应将难以跟上全球不断增长的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lme-copper-rises-to-highest-since-june-2022-as-outlook-brightens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:14:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西国家石油公司董事长被停职，导致领导层争论复杂化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/petrobras-chairman-suspended-complicating-leadership-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家法院以涉嫌利益冲突为由，暂停了巴西国家石油公司任命的董事长的职务，这是困扰该公司数周的领导权斗争的新转折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/petrobras-chairman-suspended-complicating-leadership-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 02:54:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东风险升温，金价突破 2,400 美元后下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/gold-hits-fresh-high-as-mideast-tensions-boost-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势加剧，避险资产的买盘动力增强，金价飙升至新纪录后下跌。]]></description>
